BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (him when no one else would.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td ('You know what I admire most about you?' Pip told Gritch one evening. 'You did not just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (stop being greedy. You became the most generous animal I know.') Tj ET
