BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Here is a challenge from the Sharing Tree, just for you:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (This week, try sharing something every single day. It does not have to be big.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Monday: share a smile with someone who looks sad. Tuesday: share your time by helping with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (a chore. Wednesday: share a compliment   tell someone what you like about them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (Thursday: share your food   give a friend half your cookie. Friday: share your things  ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (lend a toy or a book.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Watch what happens. Watch how sharing makes YOU feel. Watch how it makes others feel.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Watch how the garden grows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A weekly calendar showing different sharing acts for each day, drawn like a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (child's colorful planner, with small flowers growing beside each completed sharing act]) Tj ET
