BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And always remember: the Sharing Tree's greatest lesson was not just about fruit.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (It was about this: things that are hoarded die. Things that are shared multiply.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Love shared becomes more love. Joy shared becomes more joy. Kindness shared becomes more) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (kindness.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (You are a Sharing Tree too. Everything you give away comes back to you doubled.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (So share without fear. Give without counting. And grow without limits.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: A child standing with arms outstretched like tree branches, friends and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (family gathered around like animals around the Sharing Tree, love and kindness flowing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (outward and returning multiplied]) Tj ET
