BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (hug, a flower blooms on that branch.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Every time a family shares a meal, the roots grow deeper and stronger.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (The Sharing Tree lives in all of us. And as long as one person somewhere is generous, it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (will never, ever die.) Tj ET
