BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Generosity Brings More Happiness Than Keeping Things for Yourself) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (The Sharing Tree showed us that keeping everything for yourself doesn't make you happier  ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (it makes you lonely and your treasures rot. But sharing? Sharing makes everything grow.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (When you give generously, you get back more than you gave   in friendship, in love, in the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (joy of making others happy. So share your toys, share your snacks, share your time, share) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (your smile. You'll never run out of good things when your heart is generous.) Tj ET
endstream
